sql:
SELECT MAX(revenue) AS max_revenue
FROM financial_statements
WHERE fiscal_year = 2013;

SELECT AVG(revenue) AS average_revenue
FROM financial_statements
WHERE company_id = 1;

SELECT AVG(revenue) AS average_revenue
FROM financial_statements
WHERE fiscal_year = (SELECT MAX(fiscal_year) FROM financial_statements);

external_knowledge:
Operating margin = Operating income / Revenue; 
Net margin = Net income / Revenue; 
Free cash flow margin = Free cash flow / Revenue; 
Debt-to-equity ratio = Total liabilities / Shareholders' equity; 
These ratios are essential for evaluating a company's profitability, efficiency, and financial leverage.

